<p>【3】Jürgen Habermas, ‘The New Obscurity: The Crisis of the Welfare State and the Exhaustion of Utopian Energies’, in The New Conservatism: Cultural Criticism and the Historian’s Debate, ed. and trans. Shierry Weber Nicholsen (Cambridge, MA: MIT Press, 1989), pp. 48–70.</p>
